The Chronicles of Narnia talked about four siblings, who are evacuated to the countryside, where they find a wardrobe that leads to Narnia. They ally with the lion Aslan against the White Witch, who has placed Narnia in an eternal winter.
I first watched this movie around 10 years ago, It brought me an unforgettable memory. The concept of the movie is so attractive and special effects are super detailed. That the reasons why I really like this movie. 
